column1: # file_name - name of the file containing the video of the event
# date - when the video was recorded
# plant - the individual plant at which the video was recorded
# black_availability - availability of black fruits in the branch measured as an observational percentage
# no_fruits - total number of  fruits succesfully removed and usually swallowed (unless the bird leaves with the fruit on the beak to consume it other place)
# beak_trials - total number of beak trials (succesful and not succesful)
# fruit_black - number of black fruits consumed
# fruit_red - number of red frutis consumed
# fruit_NA - number of consumed fruits whose color is not appreciated.
# flight_fruit - of the bird leaves with the fruit on the beak without swallowing it first
# arrival - minute in the video of bird arrival
# departure - minute in the video with bird departure
# full_visit - if the visit is fully recorded (yes) or if it is partial (no)
# indiv_obs - observations for the specific video
